    <div class="details-sub-header-perch" > The Perch Inn, Binsey, Oxford</div>


    <p>We have arranged travel from the ceremony to the reception, which we are keeping as a surprise. This will involve a bit of walking on pathways (about 10 mins). We will guide you there straight after the ceremony.
    </p>
    <p>The reception will be at <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/The+Perch/@51.765512,-1.2895437,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x4876c42be387e3d1:0xf0dd327f99c766ad!8m2!3d51.765512!4d-1.287355" target="_blank"> The Perch Inn, Binsey Lane, Binsey, Oxford, OX2 0NG </a>. The Perch is located next to Port Meadow, approximately 2 miles from Oxford city centre. We will be in a marquee with hard flooring but there are some outdoor grassy areas too so please bear that in mind when choosing your footwear.
    </p>
    <p>A three course meal will be served at 5.30pm, followed by a band and music until midnight.
    </p>
    <p>No parking will be available for guests. However, there are lots of taxi companies in Oxford available for booking transport to leave The Perch at the end of the night - <a href="https://www.001taxis.com/" target="_blank"> 001 taxis </a> can be reached on 01865 240000, or Uber is also available.
    </p>

